      <div class="step-item">
        <div class="step-text">
          <span class="step">Step 1)</span>Code an original art piece. Learn
          from <a href="/guides">our guides</a>. For submission rules <a
            href="https://github.com/hackclub/blot/blob/main/docs/GET_A_BLOT.md"
            >read this.</a
